      "code_id": "d1702403-3a21-4ea8-bd58-bd40d5ef1110",
      "code_content": "list_a = [5, 20, 3, 7, 6, 8]\nn = int(input())\n\nlist_a = sorted(list_a)\nlist_len = len(list_a)\nres = list_a[list_len - n:]\nfor i in range(n):\n    res[i] = str(res[i])\n\nprint(\" \".join(res))\n",
